CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four women, including Mrs. Bruce Jackson wearing dark dress with light oclored lace bodice and flower at waist, standing around table with large floral arrangement in Webster Hall with light colored walls for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
